  "updated": 1782716836,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a3facdd5f21eea5d60fac9f",
      "text": "2026夏アニメ",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782557964,
      "updated": 1782557964
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3fad0b00000000000a77ae",
      "text": "[2026春アニメ] ←2026夏アニメ→ [2026秋アニメ]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782557964,
      "updated": 1782558028
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3fad2400000000000a77ee",
      "text": "作り方: [2022/03/15#62307bc36eb40600002a16e8]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782557988,
      "updated": 1782558040
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3fad5700000000000a77ef",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782558040,
      "updated": 1782558040
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3fad0b00000000000a77af",
      "text": "[これ描いて死ね]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782557964,
      "updated": 1782557964
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3ff8d900000000000b8f95",
      "text": " 伊豆大島でたくさん宣伝を見た[inajob.icon]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782577370,
      "updated": 1782577384
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3fad0b00000000000a77b0",
      "text": "[ヤニねこ]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782557964,
      "updated": 1782557964
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3fb59000000000002dcfd1",
      "text": " アニメ化……していいのかそれ……？[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782560107,
      "updated": 1782560117
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3fef9c00000000006e4363",
      "text": " 『異種族レビュアーズ』以降この手のアニメが増えてきた気がする。なんでも炎上しちゃう社会の風潮に無意識に反抗している…？[uminosachinomisokatsu.icon]",
      "userId": "69e3880c2d8712a4688ed0cf",
      "created": 1782574972,
      "updated": 1782575606
    },
    {
      "id": "6a404a420000000000b8d112",
      "text": "  異種族レビュアーズはまあええやろ(謎基準)[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782598171,
      "updated": 1782598193
    },
    {
      "id": "6a404a7e0000000000b8d113",
      "text": " [キメねこ]と勘違いしてた[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782598231,
      "updated": 1782598250
    },
    {
      "id": "6a404a920000000000b8d114",
      "text": " 　タバコ止まりならまあギリいいか……",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782598251,
      "updated": 1782598269
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3fad0b00000000000a77b1",
      "text": "[透明な夜に駆ける君と、目に見えない恋をした。]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782557964,
      "updated": 1782557964
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3fad0b00000000000a77b2",
      "text": "[乙女ゲー世界はモブに厳しい世界です2]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782557964,
      "updated": 1782557964
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3fad0b00000000000a77b3",
      "text": "[片田舎のおっさん、剣聖になるⅡ]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782557964,
      "updated": 1782557964
    },
    {
      "id": "6a41d14c0000000000e57901",
      "text": " たぶんみる[koyoshi.icon][taktamur.icon]",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1782698316,
      "updated": 1782705318
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3fad0b00000000000a77b4",
      "text": "[転校先の清楚可憐な美少女が、昔男子と思って一緒に遊んだ幼馴染だった件]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782557964,
      "updated": 1782557964
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3fad0b00000000000a77b5",
      "text": "[領民0人スタートの辺境領主様]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782557964,
      "updated": 1782557964
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3fad0b00000000000a77b6",
      "text": "[才女のお世話 高嶺の花だらけな名門校で、学院一のお嬢様(生活能力皆無)を陰ながらお世話することになりました]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782557964,
      "updated": 1782557964
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3fad0b00000000000a77b7",
      "text": "[追放された転生重騎士はゲーム知識で無双する]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782557964,
      "updated": 1782557964
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3fad0b00000000000a77b8",
      "text": "[炎の闘球女 ドッジ弾子]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782557964,
      "updated": 1782557964
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3fad0b00000000000a77b9",
      "text": "[乙女怪獣キャラメリゼ]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782557964,
      "updated": 1782557964
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3fad0b00000000000a77ba",
      "text": "[BLACK TORCH]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782557964,
      "updated": 1782557964
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3fad0b00000000000a77bb",
      "text": "[令和のダラさん]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782557964,
      "updated": 1782557964
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3fad0b00000000000a77bc",
      "text": "[いびってこない義母と義姉]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782557964,
      "updated": 1782557964
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3fad0b00000000000a77bd",
      "text": "[鬼の花嫁]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782557964,
      "updated": 1782557964
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3fad0b00000000000a77be",
      "text": "[対ありでした。～お嬢さまは格闘ゲームなんてしない～]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782557964,
      "updated": 1782557964
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3fad0b00000000000a77bf",
      "text": "[文豪ストレイドッグス わん！2]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782557964,
      "updated": 1782557964
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3fad0b00000000000a77c0",
      "text": "[花ざかりの君たちへ(第2期)]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782557964,
      "updated": 1782557964
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3fad0b00000000000a77c1",
      "text": "[レッツゴー怪奇組]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782557964,
      "updated": 1782557964
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3fad0b00000000000a77c2",
      "text": "[鎧真伝サムライトルーパー(第2クール)]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782557964,
      "updated": 1782557964
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3fad0b00000000000a77c3",
      "text": "[ここは俺に任せて先に行けと言ってから10年がたったら伝説になっていた。]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782557964,
      "updated": 1782557964
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3fad0b00000000000a77c4",
      "text": "[正反対な君と僕(第2期)]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782557964,
      "updated": 1782557964
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3ff8fd00000000000b8f96",
      "text": " 見る[inajob.icon]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782577406,
      "updated": 1782577410
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3fad0b00000000000a77c5",
      "text": "[幼女戦記Ⅱ]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782557964,
      "updated": 1782557964
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3ff90600000000000b8f97",
      "text": " 1期は見たが、どうするか、、[inajob.icon]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782577415,
      "updated": 1782577427
    },
    {
      "id": "6a404ab00000000000b8d115",
      "text": " とうとう第二期始まるのか[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782598281,
      "updated": 1782598289
    },
    {
      "id": "6a41ecaf0000000000966e60",
      "text": " これは見る[taktamur.icon]",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1782705326,
      "updated": 1782705331
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3fad0b00000000000a77c6",
      "text": "[LV999の村人]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782557964,
      "updated": 1782557964
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3fad0b00000000000a77c7",
      "text": "[魔法少女リリカルなのは EXCEEDS Gun Blaze Vengeance]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782557964,
      "updated": 1782557964
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3fad0b00000000000a77c8",
      "text": "[クレバテスⅡ-魔獣の王と偽りの勇者伝承-]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782557964,
      "updated": 1782557964
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3fad0b00000000000a77c9",
      "text": "[骸骨騎士様、只今異世界へお出掛け中Ⅱ]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782557964,
      "updated": 1782557964
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3fad0b00000000000a77ca",
      "text": "[アズールレーン びそくぜんしんっ！にっ!!]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782557964,
      "updated": 1782557964
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3fad0b00000000000a77cb",
      "text": "[無職転生Ⅲ ～異世界行ったら本気だす～]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782557964,
      "updated": 1782557964
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3fad0b00000000000a77cc",
      "text": "[株式会社マジルミエ(第2期)]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782557964,
      "updated": 1782557964
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3fad0b00000000000a77cd",
      "text": "[君のことが大大大大大好きな100人の彼女(第3期)]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782557964,
      "updated": 1782557964
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3fad0b00000000000a77ce",
      "text": "[ブチ切れ令嬢は報復を誓いました。 ～魔導書の力で祖国を叩き潰します～]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782557964,
      "updated": 1782557964
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3fad0b00000000000a77cf",
      "text": "[ヘルモード ～やり込み好きのゲーマーは廃設定の異世界で無双する～ 2nd Season]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782557964,
      "updated": 1782557964
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3fad0b00000000000a77d0",
      "text": "[手札が多めのビクトリア]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782557964,
      "updated": 1782557964
    },
    {
      "id": "6a40575b0000000000728b21",
      "text": " Webで漫画を少し読んだ、見るかなぁ[inajob.icon]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782601564,
      "updated": 1782601596
    },
    {
      "id": "6a41ab00000000000036ed14",
      "text": " ちょうど期間限定で3巻くらいまで公開してたから一気見してしまった[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782688470,
      "updated": 1782688495
    },
    {
      "id": "6a41ab19000000000036ed15",
      "text": " 　たいへんおもしろい",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1782688495,
      "updated": 1782688497
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3fad0b00000000000a77d1",
      "text": "[「きみを愛する気はない」と言った次期公爵様がなぜか溺愛してきます]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782557964,
      "updated": 1782557964
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3fad0b00000000000a77d2",
      "text": "[世界最強の後衛 ～迷宮国の新人探索者～]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782557964,
      "updated": 1782557964
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3fad0b00000000000a77d3",
      "text": "[うちの弟どもがすみません]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782557964,
      "updated": 1782557964
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3fad0b00000000000a77d4",
      "text": "[天幕のジャードゥーガル]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782557964,
      "updated": 1782557964
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3fad0b00000000000a77d5",
      "text": "[花織さんは転生しても喧嘩がしたい]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782557964,
      "updated": 1782557964
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3fad0b00000000000a77d6",
      "text": "[きみが死ぬまで恋をしたい]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782557964,
      "updated": 1782557964
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3fad0b00000000000a77d7",
      "text": "[北斗の拳 拳王軍ザコたちの挽歌(第2クール)]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782557964,
      "updated": 1782557964
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3fad0b00000000000a77d8",
      "text": "[二十世紀電氣目録-ユーレカ・エヴリカ-]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782557964,
      "updated": 1782557964
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3fad0b00000000000a77d9",
      "text": "[ふつつかな悪女ではございますが～雛宮蝶鼠とりかえ伝～]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782557964,
      "updated": 1782557964
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3fad0b00000000000a77da",
      "text": "[捨てられ聖女の異世界ごはん旅 隠れスキルでキャンピングカーを召喚しました]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782557964,
      "updated": 1782557964
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3fad0b00000000000a77db",
      "text": "[ぐらんぶる Season 3]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782557964,
      "updated": 1782557964
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3fad0b00000000000a77dc",
      "text": "[さよならララ]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782557964,
      "updated": 1782557964
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3fad0b00000000000a77dd",
      "text": "[バンドリ！ ゆめ∞みた]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782557964,
      "updated": 1782557964
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3fad0b00000000000a77de",
      "text": "[鉄鍋のジャン！]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782557964,
      "updated": 1782557964
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3ff2c300000000006e4364",
      "text": " ニコニコ動画のコメント付きで見るのが楽しみ[uminosachinomisokatsu.icon]",
      "userId": "69e3880c2d8712a4688ed0cf",
      "created": 1782575779,
      "updated": 1782575807
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3fad0b00000000000a77df",
      "text": "[岩元先輩ノ推薦]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782557964,
      "updated": 1782557964
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3fad0b00000000000a77e0",
      "text": "[グロウアップショウ ～ひまわりのサーカス団～]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782557964,
      "updated": 1782557964
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3fad0b00000000000a77e1",
      "text": "[盗掘王]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782557964,
      "updated": 1782557964
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3fad0b00000000000a77e2",
      "text": "[サンダー3]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782557964,
      "updated": 1782557964
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3fad0b00000000000a77e3",
      "text": "[メビウス・ダスト]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782557964,
      "updated": 1782557964
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3fad0b00000000000a77e4",
      "text": "[攻殻機動隊 THE GHOST IN THE SHELL(2026)]",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1782557964,
      "updated": 1782716836
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3ff93200000000000b8f98",
      "text": " これなんだっけ？再放送、、ではない？[inajob.icon]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782577458,
      "updated": 1782577473
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4000600000000000f9d4fb",
      "text": " 新シリーズらしいですよ。作画も原作に近い感じで[terang.icon]",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1782579297,
      "updated": 1782579342
    },
    {
      "id": "6a40f73c0000000000f56fff",
      "text": " 押井守版は人形遣いの台詞をなんかすごい改変してしまったので原作準拠の本シリーズに期待中[uminosachinomisokatsu.icon]",
      "userId": "69e3880c2d8712a4688ed0cf",
      "created": 1782642460,
      "updated": 1782643368
    },
    {
      "id": "6a41eccc0000000000966e61",
      "text": " [円城塔]が関わってるので正座待機[taktamur.icon]",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1782705355,
      "updated": 1782705387
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3fad0b00000000000a77e5",
      "text": "[最強出涸らし皇子の暗躍帝位争い]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782557964,
      "updated": 1782557964
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3fad0b00000000000a77e6",
      "text": "[天は赤い河のほとり]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782557964,
      "updated": 1782557964
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3fad0b00000000000a77e7",
      "text": "[BLEACH 千年血戦篇-禍進譚-]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782557964,
      "updated": 1782557964
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3fad0b00000000000a77e8",
      "text": "[ヒロイン？聖女？いいえ、オールワークスメイドです(誇)！]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
